This paper deals with the management of database schemas, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of bidirectional transformation, which is a technique commonly used in software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation of the proposed approach, which involves the use of functions, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
